# UI Layer Ownership

| Concern | Owner | Agent may edit when |
|---------|--------|---------------------|
| Entity tables/forms/states | `@repo/metadata-ui` | Wiring app routes to metadata-ui |
| Primitives (Button, Sidebar, Dialog) | `@repo/ui` primitives | Adding/using primitives — not restructuring compose/workspace |
| **Workspace shell compose** | `@repo/ui/.../compose/workspace` | **Explicit user approval only** |
| Tenant brand + lane CSS | `@repo/design-system` | Branding admin / token work |
| Auth, fetch, mutations | `apps/app` | Always for app behavior |
| Theme Studio / Storybook chrome | `apps/app/theme-studio`, `apps/storybook` | Preview and demo layout |

**Yes:** use metadata-ui for governed entity surfaces.  
**No:** do not replace shell/branding/workspace framework with metadata-ui unless that domain metadata exists and the user asked for it.
